    "body": "```go\r\nfunc calcFrom(tx *types.Transaction) common.Address {\r\n\tmsg, err := tx.AsMessage(types.LatestSignerForChainID(tx.ChainId()), nil)\r\n\tif err != nil {\r\n\t\tpanic(err)\r\n\t}\r\n\r\n\treturn msg.From()\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nIn latest version\r\n```go\r\nfunc calcFrom(tx *types.Transaction) common.Address {\r\n\tmsg, err := core.TransactionToMessage(tx, types.LatestSignerForChainID(tx.ChainId()), nil)\r\n\tif err != nil {\r\n\t\tpanic(err)\r\n\t}\r\n\r\n\treturn msg.From()\r\n}\r\n```",
