    "body": "So here's how to get the sender for a pending transaction (or really any transaction):\r\n\r\n```go\r\nsigner := types.LatestSignerForChainID(chainid)\r\n\r\ntx, err := c.TransactionByHash(context.Background(), txhash)\r\nif err != nil {\r\n    return err\r\n}\r\nsender, err := types.Sender(signer, tx)\r\nif err != nil {\r\n    return err\r\n}\r\nfmt.Println(\"tx sender:\", sender)\r\n```",
